{"tid":1266780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（重要!!!）7.1一人一個氫氣球為義士進行哀悼儀式","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T16:14:18.000Z","uid":263373,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6a7339ea4b8e06838cdaaa5d2dd942f940bad5","tid":1266780,"uid":263373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"六月又添一位抗爭亡魂，香港全城哀傷。<br />\n<br />\n惜七一當日，旗照升建制舉杯照飲！如此世道下若見惡旗高揚，200萬氣勢必難下！<br />\n<br />\n唯香港公民以藝術方式抗爭，以應對會展鐵桶一般的防御，呼籲明天(6&middot;30)港人一人一分力，合眾之功盡購全港黑及白色氣球，七月一日(後日)之早打入氦氣(俗稱氫氣)，去到灣仔能見到升旗旗桿的位置，或對岸文化中心海旁(另一可選位置)，集體在升旗禮時間8：00AM同時放黑色氫氣球，讓一片黑白色的氣球海，作為升旗禮的背景！為犧牲了的兩位年輕人爭取一場哀悼的儀式。"},{"pid":"1d1cf201305d3b094d465183537e2b409e3ef8dc","tid":1266780,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"呢個可行"},{"pid":"ba1bc061502b428be9ca19702e83a8cd1cabb77e","tid":1266780,"uid":128388,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"請傳給十個親友！一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5bmJQc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5bmJQc.png&h=66f21211&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed4ed01c9146c7edb73325041e8edfb9437d62e7","tid":1266780,"uid":56624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"推，和理非唔衝得可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce81b60c989f7c58c169bc7193eb4a875f953e2","tid":1266780,"uid":263373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.goodmoment.hk/氦氣瓶-helium-tank\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodmoment.hk%2F%E6%B0%A6%E6%B0%A3%E7%93%B6-helium-tank&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=31450edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.goodmoment.hk/氦氣瓶-helium-tank</a><br />\n<br />\n即日可取"},{"pid":"78421246136eb3fd8792407e3a888bc0b08c3b23","tid":1266780,"uid":263373,"like